name: AdventCalenderBreifing
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Get a cool daily gift everyday in December! Every year is different as well as every day! Add it to your Flash Briefing and get it automatically every day! 

-All gifts are virtual and can not be sold or traded in any way
-Gifts will only be given during December. All other days will be set to a default message stating how many days untill December 1st
-Every home will get the same thing and no persons will get anything different
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
